00:45:32.110 --> 00:45:33.910
They read each other's journals.

00:45:33.910 --> 00:45:36.150
It's almost like the secret societies

00:45:36.150 --> 00:45:39.160
of the Ourunta or Orunda.

00:45:39.160 --> 00:45:44.160
