So, to me, almost every
form of artistic knowledge

00:59:57.580 --> 00:59:58.670
that I've ever encountered

00:59:58.670 --> 01:00:00.610
is the knowledge proposition

01:00:00.610 --> 01:00:04.250
around knowledge exchanged as a gift.

01:00:04.250 --> 01:00:08.260
And that the gift in a society
is something that forces us

01:00:08.260 --> 01:00:11.530
also in this era know
a lot about economics.

01:00:11.530 --> 01:00:13.133
Right, shall we say?

01:00:14.580 --> 01:00:17.068
Artists, because the
outcome is not always known,

01:00:17.068 --> 01:00:19.600
it can't always be collected,

01:00:19.600 --> 01:00:22.080
it can't be turned into a commodity.

01:00:22.080 --> 01:00:25.313
Art is a gift, that artists
who endeavor to make it,

01:00:26.160 --> 01:00:28.970
are utilizing every
system sensory knowledge

01:00:28.970 --> 01:00:31.830
plus training, plus
skill, plus, plus, plus

01:00:31.830 --> 01:00:33.950
to find an avenue through which

01:00:33.950 --> 01:00:37.170
to keep the potency of that
knowledge, a.k.a. a gift,

01:00:37.170 --> 01:00:40.470
whether it's signs or symbols
or whatever, in motion.

01:00:40.470 --> 01:00:43.950
Because when we keep our gift in motion

01:00:44.900 --> 01:00:47.193
it continues to accrue power.

01:00:48.240 --> 01:00:50.850
So I have a quick story that
I want to describe to you

01:00:50.850 --> 01:00:52.470
because I think it goes partially

01:00:52.470 --> 01:00:55.580
to why I work in this particular way

01:00:55.580 --> 01:00:56.863
and then I'll wrap it up.

01:00:57.780 --> 01:01:00.150
And I have to kind of read
my sequences through it

01:01:00.150 --> 01:01:01.700
but it has to do with.

01:01:01.700 --> 01:01:05.810
How many of you know in
Native Plains-related,

01:01:05.810 --> 01:01:07.620
Lakota, Nokota, Dakota,

01:01:07.620 --> 01:01:10.980
Native American
traditions, the peace pipe?

01:01:10.980 --> 01:01:12.780
Do you know what it is?

01:01:12.780 --> 01:01:15.720
Okay, so a peace pipe,
in its raw materials

01:01:15.720 --> 01:01:18.250
is not a super elaborate thing.

01:01:18.250 --> 01:01:20.970
But what its job is, inside of a tribe,

01:01:20.970 --> 01:01:22.197
is that it's bestowed to a Chief.

01:01:22.197 --> 01:01:26.440
And the Chief, in the
tradition, holds the peace pipe

01:01:26.440 --> 01:01:28.360
and in that peace pipe, it's brought out

01:01:28.360 --> 01:01:31.650
at the most significant moments,
conflicts and difficulties

01:01:31.650 --> 01:01:33.153
across the tribal system.

01:01:34.170 --> 01:01:37.330
It is a point of reference,
stories are told,

01:01:37.330 --> 01:01:40.520
music is played, song lines
are song, et cetera, et cetera.

01:01:40.520 --> 01:01:42.140
And the peace pipe being present

01:01:42.140 --> 01:01:45.690
is imbued with cultural knowledge.

01:01:45.690 --> 01:01:49.190
The person who protects
that knowledge is the Chief

01:01:49.190 --> 01:01:52.750
because the knowledge has
to then be retained, shared,

01:01:52.750 --> 01:01:55.540
and it's imbued in a person
who has the discernment

01:01:55.540 --> 01:01:58.150
and consciousness and capacity to care

01:01:58.150 --> 01:02:01.650
for more than themselves
to carry that through.

01:02:01.650 --> 01:02:03.910
And it's passed across
generation to generation,

01:02:03.910 --> 01:02:05.760
generation, generation down the line.

01:02:06.710 --> 01:02:09.300
So at the point that
knowledge, in this case,

01:02:09.300 --> 01:02:12.730
living in this pipe, gets
changed fundamentally

01:02:12.730 --> 01:02:14.880
and permanently from what it is

01:02:14.880 --> 01:02:17.910
is the moment that another
system comes towards it

01:02:17.910 --> 01:02:22.563
in this case, they system
of commodity, and it's sold.

01:02:23.790 --> 01:02:25.890
Those peace pipes, in different tribes,

01:02:25.890 --> 01:02:28.980
were eventually sold for
access to reservation land

01:02:28.980 --> 01:02:32.560
without death after carnage.

01:02:32.560 --> 01:02:36.580
But this is the kind of gift
that you can only sell one time

01:02:36.580 --> 01:02:40.940
because after that, it loses
all of its knowledge power,

01:02:40.940 --> 01:02:44.120
its cultural trust and
what it's imbued to do

01:02:44.120 --> 01:02:45.653
across generational time.

01:02:46.820 --> 01:02:50.290
It becomes a commodity and from that point

01:02:50.290 --> 01:02:54.000
the raw materials later
on, in a commodity market,

01:02:54.000 --> 01:02:56.120
mean that the Native people

01:02:56.120 --> 01:02:59.070
will make a whole bunch
of small peace pipes

01:02:59.070 --> 01:03:01.090
and sell them through a commodity

01:03:01.090 --> 01:03:02.980
at the market, at the blanket,

01:03:02.980 --> 01:03:06.090
at the trinket hawking of the wares.

01:03:06.090 --> 01:03:09.300
The monetary system takes
over the gift system

01:03:09.300 --> 01:03:10.770
in this instance.

01:03:10.770 --> 01:03:14.430
And the knowledge exchange is denied

01:03:14.430 --> 01:03:16.730
to the person of the
acquisition through money

01:03:17.580 --> 01:03:21.163
from the person who
actually carries wisdom.

01:03:22.530 --> 01:03:25.650
But there's a cultural reality also

01:03:25.650 --> 01:03:28.240
in terms of what I was
describing around the arts.

01:03:28.240 --> 01:03:29.690
And this is why I work in it.

01:03:30.860 --> 01:03:33.680
If an artist decides to
take that peace pipe now

01:03:34.730 --> 01:03:36.810
and imbue it with the aesthetic integrity

01:03:36.810 --> 01:03:38.970
of finding form and meaning and value

01:03:40.090 --> 01:03:42.550
and labors with skill and intentionality

01:03:42.550 --> 01:03:46.700
and care and imaginative
realms, and manifests that now

01:03:46.700 --> 01:03:49.050
disconnected from its original history

01:03:49.050 --> 01:03:53.950
it now accrues again the
knowledge, again the possibility

01:03:53.950 --> 01:03:57.540
and again the value of becoming a gift.

01:03:57.540 --> 01:04:00.660
A gift that from that point
forward stays in motion

01:04:00.660 --> 01:04:03.550
in service to cultural knowledge.

01:04:03.550 --> 01:04:07.890
The arts are a cultural
asset and resource.

01:04:07.890 --> 01:04:11.800
And how we exchange our
knowledge can be provoking

01:04:11.800 --> 01:04:14.530
can be widely, widely received.

01:04:14.530 --> 01:04:16.830
It can be experimental and contortionist

01:04:16.830 --> 01:04:19.180
and it can be a variety of other things.

01:04:19.180 --> 01:04:20.680
But what it says is,

01:04:20.680 --> 01:04:23.270
the vulnerability of
my pursuits in thought

01:04:23.270 --> 01:04:25.600
and idea and knowledge

01:04:25.600 --> 01:04:28.520
I seek to manifest in the form of a gift

01:04:29.460 --> 01:04:31.740
that it will awaken a
perceptional capacity

01:04:31.740 --> 01:04:34.513
within your knowledge and
therefore we collaborate.

