what do we have in common?

01:13:12.250 --> 01:13:14.780
And then it's education, it's citizenship,

01:13:14.780 --> 01:13:18.780
it's the point of entry
into the public sphere.

01:13:21.430 --> 01:13:24.350
And it's interesting that in the moment

01:13:24.350 --> 01:13:26.140
when public education

01:13:26.140 --> 01:13:29.308
becomes a normative idea the world over

01:13:29.308 --> 01:13:32.920
the fundamental debates

01:13:32.920 --> 01:13:36.283
where driven by philosophical
claims on our limits.

