01:31:17.394 --> 01:31:21.220
That's why it revisits
us in different ways

01:31:21.220 --> 01:31:22.523
in different generations.

01:31:24.020 --> 01:31:26.660
- I didn't fully, totally understand

01:31:26.660 --> 01:31:28.520
the elements of the
question or I missed them

01:31:28.520 --> 01:31:31.970
or they got left in the sea of response.

01:31:31.970 --> 01:31:34.990
But I did have a response
that came to mind

01:31:34.990 --> 01:31:37.330
that I think has some relational value

01:31:37.330 --> 01:31:41.520
and that's, to me, when I
think of going to university

01:31:41.520 --> 01:31:44.100
or the pursuit of an education,

01:31:44.100 --> 01:31:46.990
there's the difference between
a pursuit of an education

01:31:46.990 --> 01:31:49.940
in order to have a
certification at the end

01:31:49.940 --> 01:31:53.440
and that certification at
the end brokers access points

01:31:53.440 --> 01:31:58.230
to a particular working life

01:31:59.610 --> 01:32:04.610
that leads, further tighten
up the screws of perfection,

01:32:05.000 --> 01:32:07.910
towards expertise, right?

01:32:07.910 --> 01:32:10.340
Really profound expertise.

01:32:10.340 --> 01:32:11.230
And that's one thing.

01:32:11.230 --> 01:32:13.680
There's also that place
where the encounter

01:32:13.680 --> 01:32:17.760
with so much other gives
us a way of recognizing

01:32:17.760 --> 01:32:21.180
elements of what makes us
feel awake to ourselves

01:32:21.180 --> 01:32:23.150
in the world, which is significant.

01:32:23.150 --> 01:32:26.790
To be pressured and stretched
in those places of choice

01:32:26.790 --> 01:32:28.960
to me, is a really important piece of it.

01:32:28.960 --> 01:32:32.980
Which can be that the path
of expertise is abandoned

01:32:32.980 --> 01:32:36.660
in service to working
in a garden in the land

01:32:36.660 --> 01:32:39.660
or doing something else that is ultimately

01:32:39.660 --> 01:32:41.570
another kind of knowledge.

01:32:41.570 --> 01:32:45.190
But how all those things are
interdependently knowable

01:32:45.190 --> 01:32:48.240
to me comes through the
frameworks of a pursuit

01:32:48.240 --> 01:32:50.003
and willingness to be educated.

