01:41:26.630 --> 01:41:30.630
So, but that thing, if you think of it.

01:41:30.630 --> 01:41:32.790
What is something that you know

01:41:32.790 --> 01:41:33.970
that you wish you didn't know?

01:41:33.970 --> 01:41:36.550
The likelihood is it would
be something very personal

01:41:36.550 --> 01:41:37.870
in your experience.

01:41:37.870 --> 01:41:40.460
What is something that you
know that you treasure knowing?

01:41:40.460 --> 01:41:41.870
Is probably something

01:41:41.870 --> 01:41:44.283
deeply personal in your experience, right?

01:41:45.440 --> 01:41:47.530
What is something that you know

01:41:47.530 --> 01:41:49.470
that you feel compelled to share

01:41:49.470 --> 01:41:52.780
is probably something
that you were both taught

01:41:52.780 --> 01:41:55.490
or gained extraordinary enjoyment from

01:41:55.490 --> 01:41:57.340
that you want to pass on.

01:41:57.340 --> 01:42:00.090
And what is the thing that
you have in your knowledge

01:42:00.090 --> 01:42:03.943
that you want to share
purely for self advancement?

01:42:06.031 --> 01:42:08.547
The crux between these
different intentions

01:42:13.850 --> 01:42:17.440
to me, the amateur place
of how do we use our hand,

01:42:17.440 --> 01:42:18.780
how do we use certain things,

01:42:18.780 --> 01:42:21.400
how do you derive both
pleasure and meaning

01:42:21.400 --> 01:42:25.280
from self discovery, self
manifestation of a hobby.

01:42:25.280 --> 01:42:28.990
Hold onto those things
that you clock in yourself

01:42:28.990 --> 01:42:30.700
because they will carry and buttress you

01:42:30.700 --> 01:42:34.980
across much more than
purely the success lines

01:42:34.980 --> 01:42:39.820
marching towards the end game
of a particular expertise.

01:42:39.820 --> 01:42:42.023
The hobbyist matters enormously.

